                option(value="" disabled selected) project type
                option(value="webdesign") Webdesign
                option(value="consultation") Consultation
                option(value="squarespace") Squarespace
              p . Here's a short 
              textarea.form-control#description(rows="1" cols="50" placeholder="description")
              p &nbsp; of what I have in mind. My budget is around &nbsp;
              .input-group
                .input-group-addon â‚¬
                input.form-control#budget(type="text" placeholder="1.000" size="7")
                .input-group-addon ,-
              p . You can reach  me at &nbsp;
                input.form-control#email(type="text" placeholder="myemail@example.com")
              p .
            button.btn.btn-primary.submit-enquiry.center-block Submit enquiry
